#+title: oriented delta complex
#+filetags: :topology:simplicial homology:

An /oriented [[id:6FB59C11-FE7F-41B9-9BF8-08D77BD8AEB5][\(\Delta\)-complex]]/ \(X\) is \(\Delta\)-complex with an
/orientation class/ which is a choice of sign for even \(n\)-simplex:
\[ [X] = \sum_{\sigma\in X_n} \pm \sigma \]
such that \(\partial[X] = 0\).
